reviewText: The Nanny is about a sadistic nanny, the children under Her care are mean and have a few tricks up their sleeves. Bette Davis is scary and so are the kids. the back and forth efforts to torment each other make the Nanny a great horrror suspense thriller. Bette was the best the Nanny proves it.

If you thought Bette Davis was scary in Whatever happened to Baby Jane?? You haven't seen anything. Davis was great as always! She ends up killing one of the children under her care. Try to catch this one if you can.
Bette was great in this movie but the boy was a total brat & no one would do anything about it. She did not kill the little girl on purpose. It was a accident.
